    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要提示：</strong>我们尚未确定抢先体验阶段支持的语言，但将根据愿望单数量优先翻译需求最高的语言。请务必将游戏加入愿望单，让我们了解玩家需求！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/7d954636d7b8edf5779a5fcf3eafcea3.poster.avif?t=1765886384\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/7d954636d7b8edf5779a5fcf3eafcea3.webm?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/7d954636d7b8edf5779a5fcf3eafcea3.mp4?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索与战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在被邪灵侵蚀的碎裂空间站，两名逃亡者（一只兔子与一台残破机器人）必须完成不可能的任务：直面邪灵源头，夺回自由与战利品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每次游玩皆独一无二</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘场景与程序生成机制。专属系统每轮生成数百万种变体，呈现震撼视觉风格与独特个性。每次体验皆为全新旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/06097ed19a1f558076fcccac6a3cb1ab.poster.avif?t=1765886384\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/06097ed19a1f558076fcccac6a3cb1ab.webm?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/06097ed19a1f558076fcccac6a3cb1ab.mp4?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集并改装武器库</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从基础爆能枪到引发混沌的维度武器，收集所有装备。在恰当时机穿越传送门抵达商人房间，与他的手下互动并升级装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>九大首领，九重关卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >九大关卡各设恐怖守门人。首领将施展独特战术彻底搅乱你的行程。这些巨兽只为达成一个目标——彻底阻断你的去路。你必须倾尽武器库所有力量才能突破重围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/718ebd689bbd72767953be61304386d0.poster.avif?t=1765886384\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/718ebd689bbd72767953be61304386d0.webm?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/718ebd689bbd72767953be61304386d0.mp4?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越传送门系统，与时间赛跑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索传送门网络，既可跳过关卡段落，亦可寻觅商铺房间。限时挑战附带排行榜，奖励最快通关者。是追求速度而错失珍贵战利品，还是花时间强化装备变得所向披靡？抉择权在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>邂逅角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深挖背景故事：洛里迪安环形枢纽究竟发生了什么？巨棒企业何时会抵达？这些幸存者又是何方神圣？旅途中遇见的每个角色都将揭示真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/64a940e89f676189fb486b89fa0f1cbd.poster.avif?t=1765886384\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/64a940e89f676189fb486b89fa0f1cbd.webm?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259390/extras/64a940e89f676189fb486b89fa0f1cbd.mp4?t=1765886384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级，升级，再升级</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发掘并强化海量特殊能力。你将选择潜行流还是坦克流？部署地雷与轨道补给，还是靠黑客手段舞动全场？通过快速圆形菜单即时切换战术配置。开局前调整装备，管理历次通关的技能加成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经典合作模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地与在线联机——两名逃亡者对抗整个世界！并肩战斗探索，共享资源，相互掩护，你们定能携手成功。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
